---
source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Count matching messages

Usage: mxr count [OPTIONS] <QUERY>

Arguments:
  <QUERY>

Options:
      --account <ACCOUNT>
      --mode <MODE>          [possible values: lexical, hybrid, semantic]
      --quiet                Print a bare integer, ignoring output format and tty detection
      --group-by <GROUP_BY>  Aggregate the query result set by a field instead of printing one count [possible values: from, list, category]
      --format <FORMAT>      [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help                 Print help
